variety by environment data using multiplicative mixed models and
adjustments for spatial field trend. *Biometrics*, 57(4), 1138–1147.

Smith, A. B., Cullis, B. R., & Thompson, R. (2005). The analysis of
crop cultivar breeding and evaluation trials: An overview of current
mixed model approaches. *Journal of Agricultural Science*, 143(6),
449–462.

Patterson, H. D., & Williams, E. R. (1976). A new class of resolvable
incomplete block designs. *Biometrika*, 63(1), 83–92.

Piepho, H.-P., & Möhring, J. (2007). Computing heritability and
selection response from unbalanced plant breeding trials. *Genetics*,
177(3), 1881–1888.
